@startuml Collaboration Diagram - Text Search
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam ArrowColor #1565C0
skinparam ArrowThickness 1
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

title Collaboration Diagram - Text Search Use Case

object User
object SearchPage
object SearchAPI
object AuthMiddleware
object QuotaManager
object QuickwitClient
object SearchLogger
object Database

User --> SearchPage : 1: interact()
SearchPage --> SearchAPI : 2: sendRequest()
SearchAPI --> AuthMiddleware : 3: validateAuth()
AuthMiddleware --> Database : 4: checkSession()
Database --> AuthMiddleware : 5: sessionData
AuthMiddleware --> SearchAPI : 6: authenticated
SearchAPI --> QuotaManager : 7: checkQuota()
QuotaManager --> Database : 8: getQuota()
Database --> QuotaManager : 9: quotaInfo
QuotaManager --> SearchAPI : 10: quotaAvailable
SearchAPI --> QuickwitClient : 11: search()
QuickwitClient --> SearchAPI : 12: results
SearchAPI --> SearchLogger : 13: logSearch()
SearchLogger --> Database : 14: saveLog()
SearchAPI --> QuotaManager : 15: updateQuota()
QuotaManager --> Database : 16: decrementQuota()
SearchAPI --> SearchPage : 17: returnResults()
SearchPage --> User : 18: displayResults()

@enduml



